content: So for question number one, what we’re seeing expanding growth and I’ll say it this way, we – this year, we had our third successful space launch, so that’s a major milestone, part of this is us coming into our own and the market seeing us as a proven system to where not just initial high risk kind of operators are signing with us, but we have national security. One is national security launches and specifically tactically responsive space support, where we’re operating in a more of an operational or a new method if you will in space.
